      "content": "加入 2ml 食用油",
      "duration_minutes": null,
      "tips": null
    },
    {
      "step": 6,
      "content": "下菜，翻拌一下，然后盖上锅盖焖 1 分钟",
      "duration_minutes": 1,
      "tips": null
    },
    {
      "step": 7,
      "content": "盛盘",
      "duration_minutes": null,
      "tips": null
    }
  ],
  "tips": [
    "不确定咸淡的情况，可以先少放盐，在出锅前尝味，考虑调整加盐",
